N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 2 ยง 70.1 - Definitions

State Regulations

The term county treasurer includes the Commissioner of

Finance of the City of New York, a county treasurer in counties outside the

City of New York and any other fiscal officer performing the functions of a
county treasurer. Notes
